&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing CPA, CPC, and CPM marketing campaigns;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong troubleshooting, analytical, and problem-solving abilities;&lt;/li&gt;
