&lt;p&gt;The Account Manager, Publisher Client Services plays a critical role in translating publisher objectives into actionable strategies, ensuring seamless execution from onboarding through optimization and growth. Working cross-functionally with Technical Operations, Product, and Supply teams, this individual helps ensure integrations run smoothly, performance goals are met, and marketplace quality remains strong. This is an opportunity for someone who thrives in a fast-paced, collaborative environment and wants to directly impact revenue and publisher satisfaction through thoughtful account stewardship and operational excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
