&lt;li&gt;Understand publisher business objectives and provide consultative, data-driven recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor performance metrics and proactively identify optimization opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Technical Operations and Product to resolve issues and improve performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support onboarding, integrations, troubleshooting, pacing, and overall account health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute market and client insights to inform product enhancements and operational improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in QBRs and present performance updates and strategic recommendations to clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
