&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Ad Operations, Account Management, and Partnerships teams to ensure seamless campaign execution and client satisfaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent TripleLift at industry events, client meetings, and conferences to build brand presence and generate new business leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
